Allright...Instructions for idiots: Rar is a compression format. Download Winrar and "unrar" the file. These files (Vob, IFO etc) you put in a "VIDEO_TS" folder and burn it onto a DVD-R... 
Insert the DVD-R into your DVD-player and press play!

For emulation on a PC you can put the files into an ISO with Ultraiso, Magiciso, Winiso or any other suitable prog.
